# 🚀 Bash DB Manager (CLI)

A terminal-based database manager built with **Bash + dialog**, enabling dynamic CRUD operations directly on MySQL databases.

> 💡 Inspired by tools like phpMyAdmin and Adminer — but fully running in a text-based interface (TUI).

---

## Features

* List database tables
* Browse data with pagination (LIMIT/OFFSET)
* Create records (dynamic INSERT)
* Edit records (auto-generated UPDATE forms)
* Delete records (with confirmation)
* Support for filtering (`WHERE`) and sorting (`ORDER BY`)
* Interactive terminal UI powered by `dialog`
* Secure login (no credential storage)
* Automatic column and primary key detection

---

